snippet.title: Nickelodeon Clickamajigs - International Toe Stubber (1995 Nickelodeon Shockwave Game)
snippet.description: Another Clickamajig by Greenblat himself, click on any of the 8 flags to get the guy to stub his toe and he'll yell in one of the 8 languages.
